@App_HostAddress = http://localhost:5281

### Health check
GET {{App_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### List all contacts
GET {{App_HostAddress}}/api/contacts
Accept: application/json

###

### Search contacts
GET {{App_HostAddress}}/api/contacts?q=mario
Accept: application/json

###

### Get contact by id (replace with a real id)
GET {{App_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a contact
POST {{App_HostAddress}}/api/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Mario",
  "lastName": "Rossi",
  "email": "mario.rossi@example.com",
  "phone": "+39 02 1234567",
  "company": "Acme S.r.l.",
  "role": "Responsabile IT"
}

###

### Update a contact (replace id with a real one)
PUT {{App_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Mario",
  "lastName": "Rossi",
  "email": "mario.rossi@acme.com",
  "phone": "+39 02 9876543",
  "company": "Acme S.r.l.",
  "role": "CTO"
}

###

### Delete a contact (replace id with a real one)
DELETE {{App_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

###
